orld.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aHualapai IndiansxLegal status, laws, etcxHistoryx20th centuryxUnited States. 0aHualapai IndiansxLegal status, laws, etczUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 0aHualapai IndiansxLegal status, laws, etc.zUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 0aIndian titlexHistoryx20th centuryxUnited States. 0aIndian titlezUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 7aLAW / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030013523740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300135237423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300135237/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles